sub_title: Head R&D Department KNMI, Professor Seismo-Acoustics TU Delft
summary: R&D manager and Professor in Geophysics (Infrasound, Seismology and Hydroacoustics). Verification of the Comprehensive Nuclear-Test-Ban Treaty (CTBT) within the Dutch National Data Center (NDC). Probing the atmosphere, solid earth and oceans with geophysical techniques. Forensic seismo-acoustics.
